    "created_at": "2016-07-07T00:05:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-07T00:05:37Z",
    "body": "To do what you are specifically looking to do detect the language from the OS using a package like [os-locale](https://www.npmjs.com/package/os-locale) and set the translations programmatically using [your own means](http://stackoverflow.com/a/228879/2223704) or a [third parties](http://i18next.com/).\n"
