    "updated_at": "2016-07-07T01:52:24Z",
    "body": "You can call `app.getLocale()` or `navigator.language` to get the locale of current system, but there is no built-in API to provide a localization solution.\n\nIf you want to reference how other projects implement i18n, [VS Code](https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode) is also a good example.\n"
